### Reg-Tech API — FI Portal Endpoints
### Login first using auth.http to get a token

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = <paste-jwt-here>

### ─── Submit FI Enrolment ───
# @name enrol
POST {{baseUrl}}/fi/enrol
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationName": "New Dublin Finance Ltd",
  "jurisdiction": "IE",
  "giin": "X1Y2Z3.00000.IE.099",
  "contactEmail": "compliance@newdublin.ie",
  "contactName": "Sean Murphy",
  "contactPhone": "+353-1-555-0123"
}

###

### ─── Check Enrolment Status ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/fi/enrolment/{{enrol.response.body.id}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Create Filing (Manual Entry) ───
# @name createFiling
POST {{baseUrl}}/fi/filings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportingPeriod": "2024",
  "filingType": "CRS"
}

###

### ─── Upload XML Filing ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/fi/filings/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="filingId"

{{createFiling.response.body.id}}
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="crs-report-2024.xml"
Content-Type: application/xml

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<CrsBody>
  <!-- Paste CRS XML content here or use test fixture files -->
</CrsBody>
--boundary--

###

### ─── List My Filings ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/fi/filings?status=DRAFT&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Get Filing Detail ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/fi/filings/{{createFiling.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Submit Filing for Validation ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/fi/filings/{{createFiling.response.body.id}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Get Notifications ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/fi/notifications?unreadOnly=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Mark Notification as Read ───
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/fi/notifications/00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000099/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
